<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id74528897-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s702"><num value="702">§ 702.</num><heading> Definition</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For purposes of this chapter, “Federal land management agency” includes—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id74528898-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s702/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> the Forest Service of the Department of Agriculture;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id74528899-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s702/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> the Bureau of Land Management of the Department of the Interior;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7452889a-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s702/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> the National Park Service of the Department of the Interior;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7452889b-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s702/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> the Fish and Wildlife Service of the Department of the Interior;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7452889c-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s702/5"><num value="5">(5)</num><content> the Bureau of Reclamation of the Department of the Interior; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7452889d-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s702/6"><num value="6">(6)</num><content> the Army Corps of Engineers.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id7452889e-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(<ref href="/us/pl/105/225">Pub. L. 105–225</ref>, <date date="1998-08-12">Aug. 12, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/1267">112 Stat. 1267</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
